_json.gridTitle: 5 Signs of End State Hashimoto's (& What it means and how to stop it)
_json.description: End stage Hashimoto's is what happens if you let Hashimoto's thyroiditis go untreated for many years. Ultimately, you will end up with an atrophied and non-functioning gland and some serious symptoms. Once your thyroid has been completely destroyed by autoimmune thyroiditis, you are no longer able to naturally treat your condition. Learn how to identify the signs of end stage Hashimoto's so you can try to prevent it from happening. Hashimoto's natural treatment | Hashimoto's therapies.
